data.description: Welcome to 3 White Oak Rd in historic Laughlintown.  Offered AS IS, a Sprawling Ranch Home like this doesn't come along every day. Be it a year-round, vacation, or investment property, this home has all the makings of a perfect retreat.  Located a few miles from the Diamond in Ligonier, and Laurel Mountain Ski Resort, you will enjoy year-round recreation, dining and shopping.  3 large bedrooms and 1.5 baths.  The living room features a beautiful brick fireplace and built in bookshelves.  An extra-large family room is a perfect gathering place for friends and family.  A perfect sunroom overlooks the private backyard, patio and hot tub where you can relax under the stars. A governor driveway, 2 car garage and an additional driveway means plenty of parking for entertaining.  New leech bed installed on September 23.  With some TLC and personal touches this could be your Laurel Mountain Dream Home.
